Author: al-Biqāʿī, Burhān al-Dīn Abu l-Ḥasan Ibrāhīm b. ʿUmar
Title: ʿUnwān al-ʿUnwān
Editor: Ḥasan Habashī
Publisher: Dār al-Kutub wa-l-Wathāʾiq al-Qawmīya
Place of Publication: Cairo
Date of Pulbication: 2010 (2nd ed.)
Volumes: 1
Words:
